prodNameC: 亞培設計師心肌肌鈣蛋白-I檢驗試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT STAT Troponin-I Reagent Pack:
MICROPARTICLES: Anti-tropnin-I
(mouse, monoclonal) coated microparticles in TRIS buffer with protein
(bovine and goat) stabilizers
CONJUGATE: Anti-tropnin-I (mouse. Monoclonal) acridinium labeled conjugate in MES buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizer.
ASSAY DILUENT: Tropnin-I Assay Diluent contains protein (bovine and goat) stabilizers in phosphate buffer.
ARCHITECT STAT Troponin-I Calibrators:
Calibrator A contains human serum, nonreactive for HBsAg. HIV-1 Ag or HIV-1 NAT. anti-HCV. and anti-HIV-1/HIV-2.
Preservative: Sodium Azide. Calibrators B through F contain a recombinant human cardiac troponin IC complex in phosphate buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizer.
ARCHITECT STAT Troponin-I Controls:
contain a recombinant human cardiac troponin IC complex in BES buffer with protein (fish and human [donor units of which have been tested and found to be nonreactive for HBsAg. HIV-1 Ag or HIV-1 NAT. anti-HCV. and anti-HIV-1/HIV-2.])
applicantName: 美商亞培股份有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民生東路三段49號5、6樓及51號5、6樓
efficacy: 利用一化學冷光微粒酵素免疫分析法(CMIA)，可定量測試人類血清或血漿中的心肌肌鈣蛋白。
